                    <p class="centerText">
                        Lunch Menu 11am - 2pm<br />
                        $11.00 includes<br /> 
                        Drink, Fries and Coleslaw <br />
                        Your Choice of :<br />
                        Cheeseburger, Hamburger, Fish Sandwich,
                        Grilled or Fried Chicken Sandwich, 
                        Sloppy Joe,
                        Grilled Cheese or 
                        BBQ Pork Sandwich 
                    </p>

                    <div class="pageDivider"></div>

                    <p class="centerText">
                        Dinner Buffet 4pm til 8pm <br />
                        $16.00 includes<br /> 
                        Drink Salisbury Steak, Fried Chicken, Fried Pork Chop
                        Mashed Potatoes, Gravy, Greens, Acre Peas, Sweet Carrots, Cream Peas, Squash & Onion
                    </p>

