                <article>
                    <p class="centerText fontSize1_Halfem topMargin1em underLine">Tuesday Menu</p>

                    <div class="width30 autoMarginLeftRight">
                        <img class="Taco_Chicken.jpg" src="~/Images/Taco_Chicken.jpeg" />
                    </div>

                    <p class="centerText">
                        Taco Tuesday 4pm-8pm<br />
                        All You Can Eat Taco Buffet $16.00
                    </p>

                    <div class="pageDivider"></div>

                    <p class="centerText">
                        Hard and soft tacos, refried beans, vegatables and sides, includes salad bar
