                    <p class="centerText">
                        Fried Chicken, Fried Pork Chops, Boston Butt
                        Rice, Gravy, Potatoes and Carrots, Greens, Acre Peas, Squash & Onions, Cream Peas, Sweet Carrots plus Our Salad Bar
                    </p>
